dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.corecommunication

Interface ISignalIPdu

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IIPdu, IPdu

    public interface ISignalIPdu
extends IEntity, IIPdu
    ISignalIPdu: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Represents the I-PDU's handled by Com. The SignalIPdu assembled and disassembled in AUTOSAR COM consists of one or more signals. In case no multiplexing is performed this IPdu is routed to/from the Interface Layer.
